txt.en: Defeat Agath-kali's guardian, Narkhor the Flensed.
Find Morloth and interrupt the Rite of Returning
Tûm Morloth can be found outside Bâr Nírnaeth, the Houses of Lamentation.\n\nAgath-kali has absconded to Tûm Morloth to begin her final preparations for Dhak Thrakrut, the Rite of Returning.

Deep in the darkness of Thuringwath lies Bâr Nírnaeth, the Houses of Lamentation. There, within that great fane where the Nazgûl once worshipped and made sacrifice to Sauron, one of the Dark Lord's most mysterious servants prepares Dhak Thrakrut, the Rite of Returning.
Defeat Agath-kali, the Mistress of Lamentation
Bâr Nírnaeth, the Houses of Lamentation -- Tier 2
Defeat Manôzagar within Mokh Núlum, the Vault of Anguish.
Agath-kali can be found in Tûm Morloth.\n\nYou must defeat Agath-kali before she can perform Dhak Thrakrut, the Rite of Returning.
Across the broken span, Agath-kali prepares a fell ritual before Morloth
